            {
                "comment": "A very good professor with only one problem. She is quite demanding, but she doesn't let you know this. Since no other history professor I've had actually demanded much, I coasted through with little effort and got a... C.",
                "difficulty_rating": 4,
                "quality_rating": 5
            },
            {
